      "layout": "The page uses a full-bleed layout without a fixed max-width, allowing content to span the browser's width, though elements frequently align to loose vertical columns or grids. The hero section features unusually large, overlapping text with an irregular arrangement of small image cards, setting a dynamic, non-uniform tone. Section rhythm is primarily driven by generous vertical spacing between content blocks. Content arrangement is fluid; sometimes text-left/image-right, but more often a collage of visual elements surrounding central textual content. The navigation is minimal, a simple top-bar with a hamburger menu.",
